{"tid":676434,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲先想入行做髮型師會否太遲?","createTime":"2018-05-24T11:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T16:22:41.000Z","uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7583afe6c695c34abd47f8f0ad9529aab07d4f1","tid":676434,"uid":28561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一屆Dse非三大IT Degree畢業<br />\n現職IT Vendors類型工作 Junior Consultant 18K<br />\n翻左一年半左右 但其實知道自己根本唔想做IT行業<br />\n一直想轉工但無決心 <br />\n拖左好耐都仲做緊宜家份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁近排突然心血來潮又諗起想翻份自己鐘意既工<br />\n其實自己由細到大都對髮型有興趣<br />\n但中學畢業又負碌入到U所以到最後都係揀翻份IT工做<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見髮型師其實係17 18歲開始入行<br />\n2年白紙 之後2年技術員(幫人染髮之類) 之後先會做見習髮型師<br />\n如果24歲先做白紙 會唔會太遲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513287210e2aa90f9d58acd6d224ba3f4d297c2a","tid":676434,"uid":159086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"唔遲 大把請人"},{"pid":"25918b72a39fcfe6e6543be34816f0ee634591eb","tid":676434,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"唔會啦 只要你係有心做 一家定做得起 太多垃圾髮型師"},{"pid":"0921512abc5e1c53ad269d189fe52869a212145a","tid":676434,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"翻工時間好長"},{"pid":"d0e8082672ece30bee0862a19aea264ea88facb2","tid":676434,"uid":76277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"只係知樓主要好大勇氣先可以放低身段"},{"pid":"2ad6d7cb44b0f04093cf1abf0de22320dfabeae7","tid":676434,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"屋企以前開髮型屋<br />\n有心唔怕遲，不過呢行要好 talkative"},{"pid":"3242493da568dade17b498e004e59c0e279f6880","tid":676434,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s